text.tspan: Change in total value of exports by country to world (% of GDP), Japan,
Figure illustrates how dyadic and national estimates of the total value of exports by country to the rest of the world compare.
Dyadic trade may not present a comprehensive account of a nation's trade activities. Aggregating partner trade does not
translate into national figures as trade flows to categories such as 'Other trading partners', amongst others, may be excluded
